<h2>查看是否有某个程序</h2>

<p>ps -ef | grep redis</p>

<p>ps -aux | grep nginx</p>

<h2>本地文件与远端同步</h2>

<p>/usr/bin/rsync -av /home/dir/ wenhua@210.28.216.96:/home/dir/&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>

<h2>查看摸个应用的进程数</h2>

<p>ps -alf|grep myprojectname|wc -l</p>

<p>jstack PID(如：28344)</p>

<h2>查看端口占用</h2>

<p>lsof -i:端口号</p>

<p>netstat -tunlp|grep 端口号</p>

